{"id":50,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":41,"title":"41. Colors","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":21,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/41-colors.50/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/0-41-colors.mp3","transcript":"Red is a vibrant color.\nRoses are sometimes red.\nBlood is red.\nWhite is the color of snow.\nClouds are very often white.\nBlue is the color of the sky and the ocean.\nBlack isn't really a color at all.\nTar is black, a crow is black.\nGreen is the color of grass.\nIt is also the color of leaves on the trees in the summer.\nBrown is the color of dirt.\nMany people have brown hair.\nYellow is a bright color.\nMost people use yellow when they draw a picture of the sun.\nOrange is an easy color to remember,\nthat is because an orange is orange.\nPink is the color that we dress baby girls in.\nWe dress baby boys in blue.\nPurple is the color of some violets.\nThe Canadian flag is red and white.\nWhat color is your flag?","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:43","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Red is a vibrant color.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/1.mp3","time_start":2.3,"time_end":4.3},{"position":2,"content":"Roses are sometimes red.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/2.mp3","time_start":4.6,"time_end":6.6},{"position":3,"content":"Blood is red.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/3.mp3","time_start":6.9,"time_end":8.3},{"position":4,"content":"White is the color of snow.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/4.mp3","time_start":8.9,"time_end":11.0},{"position":5,"content":"Clouds are very often white.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/5.mp3","time_start":11.4,"time_end":13.8},{"position":6,"content":"Blue is the color of the sky and the ocean.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/6.mp3","time_start":14.5,"time_end":17.7},{"position":7,"content":"Black isn't really a color at all.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/7.mp3","time_start":18.3,"time_end":21.0},{"position":8,"content":"Tar is black, a crow is black.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/8.mp3","time_start":21.2,"time_end":24.4},{"position":9,"content":"Green is the color of grass.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/9.mp3","time_start":25.1,"time_end":27.4},{"position":10,"content":"It is also the color of leaves on the trees in the summer.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/10.mp3","time_start":27.6,"time_end":31.2},{"position":11,"content":"Brown is the color of dirt.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/11.mp3","time_start":32.3,"time_end":34.5},{"position":12,"content":"Many people have brown hair.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/12.mp3","time_start":35.2,"time_end":37.3},{"position":13,"content":"Yellow is a bright color.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/13.mp3","time_start":38.2,"time_end":40.2},{"position":14,"content":"Most people use yellow when they draw a picture of the sun.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/14-2025-05-31-15-55-19.mp3","time_start":40.9,"time_end":45.0},{"position":15,"content":"Orange is an easy color to remember,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/16.mp3","time_start":46.1,"time_end":48.9},{"position":16,"content":"that is because an orange is orange.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/17.mp3","time_start":49.2,"time_end":52.2},{"position":17,"content":"Pink is the color that we dress baby girls in.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/18.mp3","time_start":53.0,"time_end":56.5},{"position":18,"content":"We dress baby boys in blue.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/19.mp3","time_start":56.9,"time_end":59.4},{"position":19,"content":"Purple is the color of some violets.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/20.mp3","time_start":60.1,"time_end":62.7},{"position":20,"content":"The Canadian flag is red and white.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/21.mp3","time_start":63.1,"time_end":65.9},{"position":21,"content":"What color is your flag?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/41-colors-2019-03-20-09-47-35/22.mp3","time_start":66.5,"time_end":68.4}]}